Proposed timetable:
# TravelPlan: Barcelona family trip, Aug 1-8 2026

| Day 1 — 2026-08-01 — Arrival in Barcelona | Day 2 — 2026-08-02 — Gothic Quarter and waterfront | Day 3 — 2026-08-03 — Sagrada Familia and beach | Day 4 — 2026-08-04 — Park Güell and Gràcia | Day 5 — 2026-08-05 — Montjuïc and family culture | Day 6 — 2026-08-06 — Beach and aquarium | Day 7 — 2026-08-07 — Tibidabo or relaxed city day | Day 8 — 2026-08-08 — Departure to Berlin |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **1. Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona reservation begins** [lodging] 15:00–15:15 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona, Carrer de Joan Güell 207-211, Barcelona (€1211.00) — Pre-book a family room/apartment-style stay for all 7 nights so the room is available despite the late flight arrival. Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona was selected for family-room/aparthotel style, 8.5/10 rating, good metro access in Les Corts, and €173/night live rate. — Links: [link 1](https://travelstack.nuitee.link/hotels/lp3567c?checkin=2026-08-01&checkout=2026-08-08&rooms=1&adults=4&occupancies=W3siYWR1bHRzIjo0LCJjaGlsZHJlbiI6W119XQ%3D%3D&language=de&currency=EUR) | **1. Late-night taxi transfer to hotel** [transport] 00:45–01:30 @ Barcelona El Prat Airport to Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona (€35.00) — Door-to-door taxi from BCN to Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona. Web-verified estimate: about 15–20 minutes by taxi, €30–€35, recommended for 3–4 people with luggage at this hour. — Links: [link 1](https://www.rome2rio.com/Train/Barcelona-Airport-BCN/Aparthotel-Atenea-Barcelona) | **1. Apartment breakfast** [meal] 08:00–08:45 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona (€25.00) — Breakfast in the room before a timed Sagrada Família visit. | **1. Apartment breakfast** [meal] 08:00–08:45 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona (€25.00) — Breakfast in the apartment before Park Güell timed entry. | **1. Apartment breakfast** [meal] 08:00–08:45 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona (€25.00) — Breakfast in the room before Montjuïc. | **1. Apartment breakfast** [meal] 08:00–08:45 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona (€25.00) — Breakfast in the room before waterfront day. | **1. Apartment breakfast** [meal] 08:00–08:45 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona (€25.00) — Breakfast in the room before Tibidabo day. | **1. Early checkout** [lodging] 04:40–04:50 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona (€0.00) — Check out before dawn for the early BCN departure. — Links: [link 1](https://www.aparthotelatenea.com) |
| **2. Early dinner at Berlin airport** [meal] 18:30–19:30 @ Berlin Brandenburg Airport (€60.00) — Simple pre-flight family dinner before security/boarding to avoid feeding kids late at night on arrival. | **2. Sleep in and apartment breakfast** [meal] 09:30–10:30 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona / Les Corts (€25.00) — Slow start after the post-midnight arrival. Breakfast from nearby supermarket/bakery in the apartment-style room. | **2. Metro to Sagrada Família** [transport] 08:45–09:15 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona to Sagrada Família (€6.00) — Web-verified route: Maria Cristina/L3 to Sants Estació, transfer to L5 to Sagrada Família; about 20–24 minutes total. — Links: [link 1](https://www.rome2rio.com/Train/Aparthotel-Atenea-Barcelona/Sagrada-Fam%C3%ADlia) | **2. Transit to Park Güell** [transport] 08:45–09:30 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona to Park Güell (€6.00) — Web-verified route: L3 from Maria Cristina/Les Corts to Lesseps, then Bus 116 to reduce uphill walking; total about 22–30 minutes depending on bus timing. — Links: [link 1](https://www.rome2rio.com/s/Aparthotel-Atenea-Barcelona/Park-G%C3%BCell) | **2. Transit to Montjuïc** [transport] 08:45–09:30 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona to Montjuïc (€10.00) — Metro/bus or taxi toward Montjuïc gardens; use transit for most of the trip and avoid steep long walks with children. — Links: [link 1](https://www.tmb.cat) | **2. Transit to Port Vell** [transport] 08:45–09:30 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona to Port Vell (€6.00) — Metro L3 to Drassanes or L4 to Barceloneta, then walk 10–15 minutes across Port Vell/Rambla de Mar to the aquarium. — Links: [link 1](https://www.tmb.cat) | **2. Transit to Tibidabo** [transport] 09:00–10:15 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona to Tibidabo (€20.00) — Metro/FGC plus Cuca de Llum funicular. Web check: from Aparthotel Atenea to Tibidabo is roughly 46–50 minutes with transfers; allow extra time with kids. — Links: [link 1](https://www.barcelona-tickets.com/tibidabo-park/directions-getting-there/) | **2. Taxi to Barcelona airport** [transport] 04:50–05:30 @ Aparthotel Atenea Barcelona to Barcelona El Prat Airport (€35.00) — Early taxi to BCN; taxi is recommended with children and luggage before morning transit is convenient. — Links: [link 1](https://www.rome2rio.com/Train/Barcelona-Airport-BCN/Aparthotel-Atenea-Barcelona) |
